  "text": "Besides the mentioned factors above, age at diagnosis, tumor stage, and tumor size were also found to be associated with prognosis of advanced PDAC. Most previous studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] illustrated the prognostic roles of these factors in advanced PDAC and the results of our study were consistent with their findings.",
